{"tid":331314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"涉打人案　指落口供不專心　海關督察　播警講法官是非錄音","createTime":"2017-07-22T05:30:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T13:15:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1900bd47c8ebb9f9f96c7ef1dacbfe8a9f414b0","tid":331314,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:30:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20097914&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170722\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20097914%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170722&d=2Yu%2B9NqC7gQ3dQGc9WbouP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=27e4e023\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20097914%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170722&h=0bc52544\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20097914&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170722</a><br />\n<br />\n涉打人案　指落口供不專心　<br />\n海關督察　播警講法官是非錄音<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】海關督察的妻女在籃球場打羽毛球時，疑遭籃球友欺負。督察之後赤膊踩場，涉爆粗大罵及毆打籃球友。督察否認襲擊，他辯稱警誡口供是受壓迫下錄取，又指落口供的警員不專心，與女同事談論某法官的兒子是偷警員制服的「神偷」。警員否認講是非，但督察原來偷偷錄下落口供的過程，當庭播放該段對話，警員仍矢口否認，不停重複答「唔同意」及「唔知道」。<br />\n記者：羅日昇　歐陽聯發<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n幫被告錄口供的偵緝高級警員梁勝君（譯音）。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n被告鄧軒臣（53歲）被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，指他於去年9月4日晚在元朗羅屋村附近籃球場打人。被告昨日沒有律師代表陪同，親自盤問替他錄取口供的警員梁勝君（譯音）。被告指梁替他落口供時，不時與在旁的女警聊天，包括提到自己明年退休，生肖屬虎，「係一隻好純良嘅貓科動物」，但梁否認講過這番話。<br />\n<br />\n警員矢口否認<br />\n<br />\n被告隨即表示，當天身上袋着兩部電話，其中一部的錄音功能「唔知點解」啟動了，記錄了整個落口供過程。法官批准被告播放其中5段錄音。<br />\n有警員問「打人嘅情況，有無嘢講」，對方回答「無」；警員接着問個人資料，包括地址職業和職位，與被告資料符合。被告盤問梁，錄音中的兩把聲，是否就是他倆？梁斷言：「唔同意」。<br />\n下一段錄音，兩名男女警聊天，有人說「有個法官，有幾個仔做律師，神偷，其中一個偷嘢，偷咗套沙展衫」，另一人附和「偷幫辦制服就威，全家就威先有個咁嘅仔」。梁繼續不認。被告再播帶，有人插口話「吓？上庭自辯？點解咁做」，又提及被告的女兒，裁判官這時叫證人避席，並問被告錄音內容是否可與口供紙互相印證，被告指可以。再播帶後，被告形容自己衣着「無上衫，着藍色格仔褲」，與口供紙相同。惟梁仍否認自己是錄音中的人。<br />\n於最後一段錄音中，有人追問：「如何如何，又話無嘢講？但又有嘢寫？」另一人語氣得戚回答：「咪運用我嘅調查技巧囉，keep住問，係咪先。」被告指，當時一名「朱沙展」催促梁，惟梁否認。其後控方傳召朱沙展，他聽到錄音後同樣否認其中一人是自己，聲稱沒有參與落口供，亦沒有騷擾錄口供過程。下周三續審。<br />\n案件編號：TMCC1225/17<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被告稱身上一部電話的錄音功能「唔知點解」啟動了。<br />\n資料圖片"},{"pid":"af7319c33465692227c433504742ee7236ede1d9","tid":331314,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170722/large/0720tat_3001.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170722%2Flarge%2F0720tat_3001.jpg&h=b270e689&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫被告錄口供的偵緝高級警員梁勝君（譯音）。資料圖片"},{"pid":"1523afde893f1536fb645e0f4fe3f31ee388be08","tid":331314,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170722/large/22ls3p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170722%2Flarge%2F22ls3p3.jpg&h=d5bc3a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告稱身上一部電話的錄音功能「唔知點解」啟動了。<br />\n資料圖片"},{"pid":"a1175e841637e2249e65224ea53ca642371cb792","tid":331314,"uid":39800,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:33:24.000Z","msg":"一般市民可唔可以喺呢啲新聞偷下師保護自己"},{"pid":"1ec111b12269caf5c4e81136d062d38f0ca52f65","tid":331314,"uid":112232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:33:56.000Z","msg":"幫辦撚個散仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個散仔又唔夠醒目<br />\n唔摷清楚clear 晒先開工<br />\n抵被撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8283d7a6f3438b707c2c53a0569b6ade4eede0b","tid":331314,"uid":112232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"幫辦撚個散仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個散仔又唔夠醒目<br />\n唔摷清楚clear 晒先開工<br />\n抵被撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41dae245997df575d7949282f265019914943328","tid":331314,"uid":56878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b5a9e40abd6d023a03e885cd21caae457674c1c","tid":331314,"uid":27381,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:34:51.000Z","msg":"毅俊仔又點夠大學生玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分分鐘傷人罪都靠自己打甩埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a89e6895e253094c80af07de16e1b0645202fd","tid":331314,"uid":63779,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"個海關都唔係咩好人,妻女籃球場打羽毛球仲若落去出頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a083a731a25230001951e526724298d8407d38dc","tid":331314,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:00:16.000Z","msg":"咁都唔認係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ee436b09258487534964e32dafcb8301fb896d0","tid":331314,"uid":36551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:03:49.000Z","msg":"撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92596eec2101f10af63eb1d14c50de44c8cd6947","tid":331314,"uid":40839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:06:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫辦撚個散仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個散仔又唔夠醒目<br />\n唔摷清楚clear 晒先開工<br />\n抵被撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最好兩個都收皮"},{"pid":"6fee4dc9daceace79e9c5489e495964019308ef2","tid":331314,"uid":22390,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:07:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個海關都唔係咩好人,妻女籃球場打羽毛球仲若落去出頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果個場本身冇人 係籃球場打羽毛球有乜問題？<br />\n有人打緊你都唔會咁傻走去食波餅啦？<br />\n仲有你老婆仔女比人恰 你會企係場邊食花生架？<br />\n<br />\nBtw個海關幫辦撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bcf51804565c69e244b94775d5728119a67462b","tid":331314,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:14:09.000Z","msg":"個位傷心柴會唔會臨退休先俾人革扯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f2005e214aff4a5b5d3f4cf0a93ebba89b2985b","tid":331314,"uid":58851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:30:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁都唔認係自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始唔認一定死口唔認, 判左有罪都唔認"},{"pid":"da009aa6ff4a940ebdf2df52750eaea571c50dcd","tid":331314,"uid":62506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:33:53.000Z","msg":"做好良民都要識保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c03c99cae127d1d9d7cb2404e5d2e1261c44e1","tid":331314,"uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:41:57.000Z","msg":"學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1cb6976d119e959de09581f265191b79de32f5","tid":331314,"uid":86980,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:43:32.000Z","msg":"裁判官應該即時要求庭警搜佢身<br />\n睇下佢在審訊期間有無唔知點解開左電話錄音功能"},{"pid":"516cc0506ddeadc67a82325c5b5862b751fbabb6","tid":331314,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"海關警犬互咬"},{"pid":"c9b5ca97ecd8cc6c61ec6ac965fad6a3027117a4","tid":331314,"uid":62060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":